{"chunk_id":"doc_quartz#chunk_001","doc_id":"doc_quartz","text":"石英是常见的硅酸盐矿物，主要化学成分是二氧化硅 SiO2。","source":"MiniGeo curated mineral notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/quartz","page":null,"topic":"concept","mineral":"quartz","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_quartz#chunk_002","doc_id":"doc_quartz","text":"石英常见强拉曼峰接近 464 cm-1，可作为识别石英的重要光谱证据。","source":"MiniGeo curated spectroscopy notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/quartz-raman","page":null,"topic":"spectroscopy","mineral":"quartz","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_quartz#chunk_003","doc_id":"doc_quartz","text":"石英硬度通常高于方解石，适合与碳酸盐矿物做性质对比。","source":"MiniGeo curated mineral notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/quartz-hardness","page":null,"topic":"mineral_property","mineral":"quartz","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_feldspar#chunk_001","doc_id":"doc_feldspar","text":"长石是一类铝硅酸盐框架矿物，常见于火成岩和变质岩。","source":"MiniGeo curated mineral notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/feldspar","page":null,"topic":"mineral_property","mineral":"feldspar","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_feldspar#chunk_002","doc_id":"doc_feldspar","text":"长石与石英同属硅酸盐体系，部分框架振动特征可能接近，弱峰和噪声会增加混淆风险。","source":"MiniGeo curated spectroscopy notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/feldspar-spectra","page":null,"topic":"spectroscopy","mineral":"feldspar","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_calcite#chunk_001","doc_id":"doc_calcite","text":"方解石是典型碳酸盐矿物，不属于硅酸盐矿物。","source":"MiniGeo curated mineral notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/calcite","page":null,"topic":"concept","mineral":"calcite","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_calcite#chunk_002","doc_id":"doc_calcite","text":"方解石的碳酸根特征带常接近 1085 cm-1，可用于与石英区分。","source":"MiniGeo curated spectroscopy notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/calcite-spectra","page":null,"topic":"spectroscopy","mineral":"calcite","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_calcite#chunk_003","doc_id":"doc_calcite","text":"方解石硬度低于石英，且遇稀盐酸常发生起泡反应。","source":"MiniGeo curated mineral notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/calcite-acid","page":null,"topic":"mineral_property","mineral":"calcite","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_hematite#chunk_001","doc_id":"doc_hematite","text":"赤铁矿是铁氧化物矿物，不是硅酸盐矿物，也不是碳酸盐矿物。","source":"MiniGeo curated mineral notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/hematite","page":null,"topic":"concept","mineral":"hematite","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_hematite#chunk_002","doc_id":"doc_hematite","text":"赤铁矿谱图常体现铁氧化物相关特征，可用于解释铁氧化物样本识别。","source":"MiniGeo curated spectroscopy notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/hematite-spectra","page":null,"topic":"spectroscopy","mineral":"hematite","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_spectroscopy#chunk_001","doc_id":"doc_spectroscopy","text":"光谱证据通过峰位、特征带和峰形支持矿物识别，也可用于分析分类混淆。","source":"MiniGeo curated spectroscopy notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/spectroscopy","page":null,"topic":"spectroscopy","mineral":"","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_spectroscopy#chunk_003","doc_id":"doc_spectroscopy","text":"单个弱峰可能受噪声、基线漂移或其他矿物峰重叠影响，证据不足时不应给出确定结论。","source":"MiniGeo curated spectroscopy notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/spectral-uncertainty","page":null,"topic":"spectroscopy","mineral":"","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_system#chunk_001","doc_id":"doc_system","text":"RAG 回答返回 chunk id 可以让答案证据来源可追踪，便于检查引用是否支持结论。","source":"MiniGeo system design notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/system-citations","page":null,"topic":"system","mineral":"","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_system#chunk_002","doc_id":"doc_system","text":"公开资料进入语料库时应记录 URL 和 license，以控制来源追踪和版权风险。","source":"MiniGeo system design notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/data-license","page":null,"topic":"system","mineral":"","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_system#chunk_003","doc_id":"doc_system","text":"Benchmark reference answer 不应直接作为 SFT 输出训练，以降低 benchmark 泄漏风险。","source":"MiniGeo system design notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/leakage","page":null,"topic":"system","mineral":"","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_system#chunk_004","doc_id":"doc_system","text":"MiniGeo 的贡献是 benchmark、RAG、证据验证和数据分析闭环，而不是训练新的地学基础模型。","source":"MiniGeo system design notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/positioning","page":null,"topic":"system","mineral":"","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_system#chunk_005","doc_id":"doc_system","text":"失败案例分析应区分数据缺失、检索失败、生成错误、验证误判和 SQL 错误。","source":"MiniGeo system design notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/failure-analysis","page":null,"topic":"system","mineral":"","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_system#chunk_006","doc_id":"doc_system","text":"Agent 最终答案同时返回 SQL 和证据，可以提高结构化数据结论和地学解释的可追踪性。","source":"MiniGeo system design notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/agent-report","page":null,"topic":"system","mineral":"","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_system#chunk_007","doc_id":"doc_system","text":"Verifier 的 supported 表示 claim 被证据支持，insufficient_evidence 表示当前证据不足以支持回答或 claim。","source":"MiniGeo system design notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/verifier-labels","page":null,"topic":"system","mineral":"","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_system#chunk_008","doc_id":"doc_system","text":"QLoRA 应在 benchmark 和 RAG 稳定后进行，否则无法判断微调是否真正提升可靠性。","source":"MiniGeo system design notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/sft-order","page":null,"topic":"system","mineral":"","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_system#chunk_009","doc_id":"doc_system","text":"混合检索结合词项匹配和语义匹配，预期比单一 BM25 有更高证据召回率。","source":"MiniGeo system design notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/hybrid-retrieval","page":null,"topic":"system","mineral":"","license":"public"}
{"chunk_id":"doc_system#chunk_010","doc_id":"doc_system","text":"Latency 是系统可用性评估的一部分，反映端到端响应成本。","source":"MiniGeo system design notes","url":"https://example.org/minigeo/latency","page":null,"topic":"system","mineral":"","license":"public"}

